                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Richmond Va</placeName>, <date>Octr 24<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                        >th</hi> 1858</date></p>\n            <p>My dear Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Please send me by first<lb/> opportunity a dozen copies of your<lb/>\n                Hebrew primers, I mean the first<lb/> book beginning with the alphabet,\n                <add>?</add><lb/> I do not recollect the exact name.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">All here with me unite in<lb/> kind regards, &amp; with best\n                wishes,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Remain,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Yours faithfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">G<add>?</add> Jacobs</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>I married a couple last eveningâ€”<persName>Mr Schaas</persName><lb/> to a\n                    <persName>Miss Stern.</persName></p>"
                  },
